{"id": 611, "genre": 1001, "title": "二胎政策全面放开，你想说啥？", "description": "你生吗？", "record_count": 6696, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021835503pJPuqFlzI4e17Z8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-30T10:07:28Z", "options": [{"id": 22016, "content": "哦=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122150}, {"id": 21251, "content": "作为一个男人，我觉得生孩子太疼了，还是尊重老婆（作为一个单身狗也就想想）的意愿，就算不生也无所谓。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224845}, {"id": 21252, "content": "是二胎，还是二孩？二胎来个三胞胎也是不错的选择！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275003}, {"id": 21255, "content": "单身女子再也不会有用人单位敢用了。看来我们能选择的只有女结婚员或女打字员。呵呵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276082}, {"id": 21256, "content": "单身女子再也不会有用人单位敢用了。看来我们能选择的只有女结婚员或女打字员。呵呵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276082}, {"id": 21512, "content": "国家以前是没钱养年轻人，现在是没钱养老人，但是有钱给非洲兄弟修铁路~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265403}, {"id": 22282, "content": "老人看来是不想管了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285537}, {"id": 21260, "content": "计生委这个东东真心没用了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219855}, {"id": 21261, "content": "生或不生！这是个问题！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186943}, {"id": 21517, "content": "一个问题的解决代表另一个难题的诞生。凡是存在的必是合理的，人为破坏只会越来越糟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159875}, {"id": 21773, "content": "终于可以见天日了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235474}, {"id": 23565, "content": "我爸已经有二胎了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292929}, {"id": 21262, "content": "那还等什么，我快有一个比我小的舅舅了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276124}, {"id": 21263, "content": "中国人在还没有完全富起来前就已经老了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232042}, {"id": 21519, "content": "国家欠我一个姐…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278262}, {"id": 21264, "content": "中国快炸了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92856}, {"id": 23058, "content": "谁喜欢谁生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290286}, {"id": 21780, "content": "生二胎？开玩笑，说的好像可以养的起似的、怎么不开二夫？还能多个人养家……", "image": "img/option/option/201606052118232LMDwpzbh9tET3Aq.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281552}, {"id": 21525, "content": "一个都不知道怎么养呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278359}, {"id": 21270, "content": "天子牧羊剪羊毛。原来的羊群老了不出毛了，让你们多来几头小羊更新一下增增产，哪儿那么多抱怨~~\r\n谢主隆恩就可以了。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211445fNUY80aykWzBqcLH.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139359}, {"id": 21271, "content": "二胎不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260227}, {"id": 21528, "content": "一直认为独生子女的生活方式是不完美的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278431}, {"id": 21273, "content": "党国改变了游戏的盈利模式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276173}, {"id": 21274, "content": "三十多了，一胎都没有，还能考虑二胎？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241415}, {"id": 21275, "content": "什么鬼。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276223}, {"id": 21276, "content": "恭喜你，再来一胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272556}, {"id": 21278, "content": "可以可以", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211506fKwMzeqFtDA1UiTG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275952}, {"id": 22046, "content": "什么时候开放三胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267817}, {"id": 21279, "content": "好像你有对象似的→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246101}, {"id": 22815, "content": "首先得有个媳妇，马上神棍节了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211187}, {"id": 21282, "content": "大前提是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158552}, {"id": 21283, "content": "老龄化社会，延迟退休。我们80后的负担已经那么大。你这时候放开二胎，准备逼死我们。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276262}, {"id": 21285, "content": "又没有优惠政策，就叫群众生，负担全在自己身上了，而且这样女性以后还能好好上班吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234209}, {"id": 21541, "content": "发现好多人拒酒开始拿二胎当理由了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237878}, {"id": 21286, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276246}, {"id": 21287, "content": "首先要有一个对象。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178863}, {"id": 21543, "content": "先给我女朋友再说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278751}, {"id": 21288, "content": "其实如果没有相应的配套设施谁会q去生第二个、第一个都没养好呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276307}, {"id": 21544, "content": "生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172437}, {"id": 21289, "content": "二胎政策就是摆设，79后想生不敢生，80后都是独生子女原来就能生，90后一个都不想生。开放不开放根本影响不了绝大多数人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276306}, {"id": 21290, "content": "就算四胎都跟我没关系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276298}, {"id": 21291, "content": "国家欠我一个哥哥?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273278}, {"id": 22059, "content": "激动啥，一胎都不一定是你的，还二胎！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283858}, {"id": 21292, "content": "退钱?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273297}, {"id": 22060, "content": "没有相关扶持政策，放开增长形势也不容乐观", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158682}, {"id": 21549, "content": "中国的女人不够了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278906}, {"id": 45613, "content": "你对自己的基因是有多自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 21294, "content": "第一个孩子都没打算要，让他来天朝，我心疼，遭不起那个罪", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276118}, {"id": 21295, "content": "我们80后真是起承转合的一代，出生的时候不让有兄弟姐妹，因为人多，到了结婚生子的时候又因为国家人少，多生。好吧，其实我想说，我与祖国同在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246400}, {"id": 21553, "content": "先让我生一胎吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278955}]}